<div id="WelcomeDiv" style="font-size:160%;padding:0.1em 0;margin:0.2em 0 -0.5em"><span class="MainTopText"><a href="/MarioWiki:Introduction" title="MarioWiki:Introduction">Welcome to the <b>Super Mario Wiki</b>!</a></span></div>
<div id="WithText" class="MainTopText">with <a href="/Special:Statistics" title="Special:Statistics">35,756</a> <a href="/Special:AllPages" title="Special:AllPages">articles</a> covering <i><a href="/Super_Mario_(franchise)" title="Super Mario (franchise)">Super Mario</a></i> and <a href="/MarioWiki:Coverage" title="MarioWiki:Coverage">more</a></div>
<p id="linksRow1" style="font-variant:small-caps;margin:-9px 10px 0"><a href="/MarioWiki:Links" title="MarioWiki:Links"><span title="Other websites about the red-capped plumber">Links</span></a> | <a href="/MarioWiki:Glossary" title="MarioWiki:Glossary"><span title="Terms used around the wiki">Glossary</span></a> | <a href="/MarioWiki:Maintenance" title="MarioWiki:Maintenance"><span title="Help us maintain various aspects of the wiki">Maintenance</span></a> | <a href="/MarioWiki:About" title="MarioWiki:About"><span title="A quick overview of the wiki and how you can join">About</span></a> | <a href="/Help:Contents" title="Help:Contents"><span title="The place to find out">Help</span></a></p>
