<p id="iconsRow3" style="margin:5px 10px 0"><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/mariowiki.com" title="Follow us on Bluesky" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img alt="Follow us on Bluesky" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/5/5e/Bluesky_icon.svg" decoding="async" loading="eager" width="24" height="24" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/smwiki" title="Like us on Facebook" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img alt="Like us on Facebook" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/1/1b/Facebook_icon.svg" decoding="async" loading="eager" width="24" height="24" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a><a href="https://www.marioboards.com/" title="Our official forum, with a lot to discuss"><img alt="Our official forum, with a lot to discuss" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/8/8c/Mushroom.png/24px-Mushroom.png" decoding="async" loading="eager" width="24" height="24" srcset="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/8/8c/Mushroom.png/36px-Mushroom.png 1.5x, https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/8/8c/Mushroom.png/48px-Mushroom.png 2x" data-file-width="1850" data-file-height="1829" /></a><a href="/MarioWiki:Discord_servers" title="Chat with us on Discord"><img alt="Chat with us on Discord" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/9/9f/Discord_icon.svg" decoding="async" loading="eager" width="24" height="24" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@MarioWiki" title="Subscribe to us on YouTube" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img alt="Subscribe to us on YouTube" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/4/4f/YouTube_icon.svg" decoding="async" loading="eager" width="24" height="24" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a><a href="https://x.com/SMWikiOfficial" title="Follow us on X" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img alt="Follow us on X" src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/c/cc/X_icon.svg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="24" height="24" data-file-width="512