<td style="width:60%;padding:0 10px 0 0">
<table id="featured" class="mainpagebox">
<tbody><tr>
<th>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Featured_article">Featured article</span></h2>
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td style="position:relative">
<div style="padding:3px 8px 2px">
<div style="margin-bottom:1.66em"><div class="mainpage-image-wrapper" style="float:left;clear:left;background:#fff;--darkbg:#222;border:1px solid #3B587E;margin:0 0.7em 0.2em 0">
<a href="/File:MKSC_Box_Art.png" class="image"><img alt="The North American box art for Mario Kart: Super Circuit." src="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/6/61/MKSC_Box_Art.png/120px-MKSC_Box_Art.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="120" height="120" srcset="https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/6/61/MKSC_Box_Art.png/180px-MKSC_Box_Art.png 1.5x, https://mario.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/6/61/MKSC_Box_Art.png/240px-MKSC_Box_Art.png 2x" data-file-width="720" data-file-height="720" /></a></div>
<i><b><a href="/Mario_Kart:_Super_Circuit" title="Mario Kart: Super Circuit">Mario Kart: Super Circuit</a></b></i> is a racing game for the <a href="/Game_Boy_Advance" title="Game Boy Advance">Game Boy Advance</a>, published by <a href="/Nintendo" title="Nintendo">Nintendo</a> and developed by <a href="/Intelligent_Systems" title="Intelligent Systems">Intelligent Systems</a>. It is the third entry in the <i><a href="/Mario_Kart" title="Mario Kart">Mario Kart</a></i> series and the first one to be released for a handheld, as well as the second <i><a href="/Super_Mario_(franchise)" title="Super Mario (franchise)">Super Mario</a></i> franchise game and third overall Nintendo-published game released for the system. The game was released in 2001, on July 21 in Japan, August 27 in North America, and September 7 and 14 in Australia and Europe respectively. <i>Mario Kart: Super Circuit</i> combines the elements from its <a href="/Super_Nintendo_Entertainment_System" title="Super Nintendo Entertainment System">Super NES</a> and <a href="/Nintendo_64" title="Nintendo 64">Nintendo 64</a> predecessors, with the key feature of the <i>Mario Kart</i> series being the usage of items obtained from <a href="/Item_Box" title="Item Box">Item Boxes</a> in order for the operator to gain an advantage over the opponents being retained; additionally, it contains all the courses from <i><a href="/Super_Mario_Kart" title="Super Mario Kart">Super Mario Kart</a></i>. <i>Mario Kart: Super Circuit</i> allows up to four players to play the game through the Game Link Cable, including a more restricted multiplayer mode that only requires one <a href="https://niwanetwork.org/wiki/Game_Pak#Game_Boy_Advance" class="extiw" title="nwiki:Game Pak">Game Pak</a>.</div>
<div class="noprint" style="float:right;position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;padding:0 17px 2px 0"><b><a href="/MarioWiki:Featured_articles" title="MarioWiki:Featured articles">More featured articles...</a></b></div>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<table id="poll" class="mainpagebox">
<tbody><tr>
<th>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Community_poll">Community poll</span></h2>
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td>
<div style="text-align:left;padding:3px 8px 2px 5px">
<div id="poll-container"><div id="polltable" style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap">
<div class="crowdsignal" style="flex-basis:300px; flex-shrink:1; flex-grow:1"><script>window.answerOtherHTML=undefined</script><script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8" src="https://secure.polldaddy.com/p/17093404.js"></script><noscript><a href="https://poll.fm/17093404">Link to poll</a></noscript></div>
<div class="awardspolls" style="display:none; flex-basis:300px; flex-shrink:1; flex-grow:1">
<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100% !important">
<tbody><tr>
<th class="marioawards" style="background-color:#c55;height:0;text-align:center"><a href="/MarioWiki:Anniversary" title="MarioWiki:Anniversary"><span style="color:white">Mario Awards XX</span></a>
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td class="cpf-container" style="vertical-align:top;width:50%;padding:0"><div class="pollspinner" style="margin-top: 1px;">
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M1. Favorite Major Character</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best recurring character prominently featured throughout the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099414"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M2. Favorite Supporting Character</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best Mario franchise character who is part of the supporting cast. This includes recurring minor characters, as well as major characters that only appeared in one game. This award does not include characters primarily from RPGs, as they have their own award.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099437"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M3. Favorite RPG Character</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best character who appears primarily in RPG titles.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099447"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M4. Favorite Guest Appearance</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best appearance of a character originating outside of the Mario franchise in media exclusively centered on the Mario brand.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099453"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M5. Favorite Power-up</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The most interesting, useful, or otherwise liked item or transformation available in the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099464"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M6. Favorite Musical Track</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best musical track from the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099485"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M7. Favorite Soundtrack</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The game or other media with the best musical tracks.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099507"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M8. Favorite Game Mechanic</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best feature in a title's gameplay. These mechanics should be specific to a game or game series, and help shape a game or game series' identity.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099562"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M9. Favorite Bowser Battle</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best boss battle with Bowser found in the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099572"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M10. Favorite Non-Bowser Boss Battle</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best boss battle found in the Mario franchise. This does not include battles with Bowser, who has his own award.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17099587"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M11. Favorite Bananza Layer</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best layer appearing in Donkey Kong Bananza.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103019"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M12. Favorite DK Game</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best game in the Donkey Kong franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103037"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M13. Favorite Mario Kart Item</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best item used in the Mario Kart series.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103050"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M14. Favorite Mario Kart Course</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best race course featured in the Mario Kart series. This does not include battle courses.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103062"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M15. Favorite Mario Party Minigame</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best minigame featured in the Mario Party series.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103078"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M16. Favorite Extra Mode</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best game mode or challenge that is auxiliary to the scope of the game's main objectives or campaigns. This does not include individual minigames, but may include collections if presented as a mode.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103092"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M17. Favorite Remake</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best new version, reissue, or remake of a game.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103100"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M18. Favorite Non-game Media</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best piece of Mario-related media that is not a game.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103109"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M19. Biggest Guilty Pleasure</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best piece of Mario media that is generally perceived as low quality, that one can nonetheless enjoy.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103133"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-1"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">M20. Favorite Game of All Time</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The best game in the greater Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103152"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F1. Most Unremarkable Game</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The game that is considered the most mediocre. They might not be impressively poor, but are notable for how uninteresting, middling, or forgettable they are.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103199"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F2. Worst Obstacle</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The least favorite non-enemy obstacle which hinders the player’s progress encountered in the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103243"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F3. Worst 3D Mission Concept</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The worst recurring mission objective found in a 3D platformer.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103247"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F4. Worst Game Mechanic</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The worst feature in a title's gameplay.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103264"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F5. Worst Boss Battle</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The least favorite boss battle found in the Mario franchise.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103268"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F6. Worst Mario Kart Course Remake</div><div class="cpf-dossier">Courses that reappeared in later installments of the Mario Kart series, but didn't do their original versions justice or improve upon them.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103392"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F7. Worst Mario Party Board</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The worst playable board in a Mario Party game.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103416"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F8. Worst Game Aesthetic</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The game in the Mario franchise with the worst visual design or overall presentation.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103435"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F9. Worst Remake</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The worst new version, reissue, or remake of a game.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103534"></div></div>
<div class="pollspinnerbox cpf-poll cpf-theme-2"><div class="cpf-header"><div class="cpf-title">F10. Most Embarrassing Nintendo Moment</div><div class="cpf-dossier">The most embarrassing, incomprehensible, or otherwise humiliating thing Nintendo has done. These are not Nintendo's most immoral moments, but rather moments which demonstrate a lack of foresight, care, or understanding of how they would appear to their audience.</div></div><div class="pollspinner&#95;poll" data-pollid="17103562"></div></div>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>
<div class="noprint plainlinks" style="float:right;padding:0;margin:-1.07em 8px 2px 0"><br /><span id="poll-extra-links"><b><a href="https://www.marioboards.com/threads/45007/latest" class="extiw" title="mb:threads/45007/latest">Discuss</a></b> • <b><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEtpPM1A4tEmc2LpFtEkux-pnthkVxsJqPxXBGtVLdORaLyQ/viewform">Submit poll</a></b> • </span><b><a href="/MarioWiki:Polls" title="MarioWiki:Polls">Archive...</a></b></div>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
